text: Nothospondias staudtii is a species of plant in the Simaroubaceae family. It is found in Cameroon, Ivory Coast, Gabon, Ghana, and Nigeria. ==References== staudtii Category:Flora of Cameroon Category:Flora of Ivory Coast Category:Flora of Gabon Category:Flora of Ghana Category:Vulnerable flora of Africa Category:Taxonomy articles created by Polbot
